Name: Ok I Pull Up
About the game: Pull up as a baby capybara in this 3D rage platformer! You, a capybara, must use your jumping skills to escape the quarantined tree tower. Explore a seamless world, split into three unique levels. Reach the end of the tower and claim unimaginable rewards. Challenging, skill-based gameplay Climb the tower only by jumping Miss a jump, fall, and lose all your progress Start all over again Cute theme with memorable side characters Several fun platforms and challenging obstacles This game will test your patience to the extreme. Good luck. *This game is a student project created over a period of 9 weeks
